== Installation ==

The recommended installation procedure is installing by fastboot by following the [[Installation guide|Installation Guide]].

== How to enter flash mode ==
Recovery: {{Button|Power}} + {{Button|Volume Up}}

Fastboot: {{Button|Power}} + {{Button|Volume Down}}
== Installation ==
# Follow the [[Installation guide|Installation Guide]] up to the 'pmbootstrap flash' part.
# Execute following line to unlock flashing: <source lang="shell">$ fastboot oem unlock-go</source>
# Follow the installation guide again.

